    "description": "《末日的旋转城堡》具有创新的轻塔防机制，在这款Roguelite游戏中你将指挥一座能飞行穿越各个大陆的城堡，利用城堡可以旋转的机制，升级城堡，装备防御塔，使用技能以抵御异魔，抵达传说中的伊甸圣地！<br>QQ群：392315989<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/51b4b9ef21996dd4694a90497785c291.avif?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=226 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/eb8e2af93370167b41c13fb58a4bd573.webp?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>· 独特的旋转塔防机制，带来独特的战斗体验!<br>· 多样的防御塔、核心技能、城防模块，截然不同的组合构筑.<br>· 各具特色的敌人种类，有趣的地图机关，丰富的战斗策略.<br>· 每一局都是随机的数据，每次游戏都是新的开始.<br><br><br><br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/c06f5eb1e179c6e3720341a4bc71f41e.webp?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>旋转城堡，把防御塔转向最合适的位置，利用城墙，抵御或撞击来袭的异魔。在合适的时机释放技能，扭转局势！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/6d84bbd754b80d1854b1902a93ee0acb.poster.avif?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/6d84bbd754b80d1854b1902a93ee0acb.webm?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/6d84bbd754b80d1854b1902a93ee0acb.mp4?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/2d3c88f06e309140908bc28f66cf5ee5.webp?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>游戏中可以获得不同的防御塔、核心技能以及城防模块，不同的装备组合能带来完全不同的战斗体验。根据他们的特性以及你的战斗风格，找到专属于自己的城堡配置！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/aa973c48925604b13ddcad901a80f103.poster.avif?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/aa973c48925604b13ddcad901a80f103.webm?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/aa973c48925604b13ddcad901a80f103.mp4?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/cb0829b88958c2833bd8be39e5850dcc.webp?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>每块大陆都分布着不同的路线节点，合理的规划与探索，获得奖励并且升级你的城堡和装备。没有一条路线是完美的，合理取舍与规划才是继续前进的关键！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/e3a421539dca62c15f784678159d343c.poster.avif?t=1743586870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/e3a421539dca62c15f784678159d343c.webm?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316680/extras/e3a421539dca62c15f784678159d343c.mp4?t=1743586870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
